          <mainBody>
            <p eId="annex_3_p_10"><b>Annex C – Progress of Bill Table</b></p>
            <blockContainer>
              <num>360 </num>
              <p>This Annex shows how each section and Schedule of the Act was numbered during the passage of the Bill through Parliament.</p>
